ong</a></h3>\n						<p>Technical 1 Manager</p>\n					</div>\n										<div class=\"item col-md-4 col-sm-6 text-center\">\n						<a href=\"http://giza.com.vn/leader/ha-anh-tuan/\"><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://giza.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/anh-tuantech-150x150.png\" class=\"img-circle wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" /></a>\n						<h3><a href=\"http://giza.com.vn/leader/ha-anh-tuan/\">Ha Anh Tuan</a></h3>\n						<p>Technical 2 Manager</p>\n					</div>\n										<div class=\"item col-md-4 col-sm-6 text-center\">\n						<a href=\"http://giza.com.vn/leader/dang-tran-hieu/\"><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://giza.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/ab3285299a5774092d46-150x150.jpg\" class=\"img-circle wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" /></a>\n						<h3><a href=\"http://giza.com.vn/leader/dang-tran-hieu/\">Dang Tran Hieu</a></h3>\n						<p>Purchasing Manager</p>\n					</div>\n										<div class=\"item col-md-4 col-sm-6 text-center\">\n						<a href=\"http://giza.com.vn/leader/nguyen-tai-tuyen/\"><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://giza.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cf84bd42593cb762ee2d-150x150.jpg\" class=\"img-circle wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" /></a>\n						<h3><a href=\"http://giza.com.vn/leader/nguyen-tai-tuyen/\">Nguyen Tai Tuyen</a></h3>\n						<p>Construction Manager</p>\n					</div>\n								</div>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n\n	<div id=\"services\" class=\"container service-list\">\n		<div class=\"row\">\n			<div class=\"section-title col-md-12 text-center text-uppercase\">\n				<h2>Services</h2>\n				<p>Our skills and experiences guarantee your success</p>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n\n		<div class=\"row\">\n									<div class=\"item col-md-3 col-sm-6 text-center\">\n						<img width=\"100\" height=\"100\" src=\"http://giza.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/icon-wrench.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" />						<h4 class=\"text-uppercase\"><a href=\"http://giza.com.vn/service/maintenance/\">Maintenance</a></h4>\n						<p>We continue to serve our project owners in many ways to make sure every aspect of the project meets their full expectations, and so that our post construction services serve as the bridge to our next project.\r\nOur post construction services include Management of warranty period through single point-of-contact for all warranty calls; Remediation, repairs, calibrations and adjustments to bring systems to full acceptance levels</p>\n					</div>\n										<div class=\"item col-md-3 col-sm-6 text-center\">\n						<img width=\"100\" height=\"100\" src=\"http://giza.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/icon-config.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" />						<h4 class=\"text-uppercase\"><a href=\"http://giza.com.vn/service/epc/\">MEP</a></h4>\n						<p>Our Mechanical &#038; Electrical (M&#038;E) Division has been a one-stop solution provider addressing all facets from design &#038; build to construction &#038; maintenance of electro-mechanical (MEP) works. Our core services include:\r\nHVAC system (Heating, ventilation, and air conditioning); Mechanical installations; Electrical installations; Fire protection; Water, Drainage and Plumping; Lighting; </p>\n					</div>\n										<div class=\"item col-md-3 col-sm-6 text-center\">\n						<img width=\"100\" height=\"100\" src=\"http://giza.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/icon-crop.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" />						<h4 class=\"text-uppercase\"><a href=\"http://giza.com.vn/service/design-supervision-consultancy/\">Design and Build</a></h4>\n						<p>At Giza E&#038;C, we assume all responsibility for your project assembling a cohesive team including the architect, engineers, and designers with whom we collaborate to develop a facility to meet your needs and expectations. As a result of using this single contract, the design, engineering and construction process is streamlined which will usually save time and money for our clients.</p>\n					</div>\n										<div class=\"item col-md-3 col-sm-6 text-center\">\n						<img width=\"100\" height=\"100\" src=\"http://giza.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/icon-chart.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" />						<h4 class=\"text-uppercase\"><a href=\"http://giza.com.vn/service/investment-consultancy/\">General contracting</a></h4>\n						<p>Our General Contracting services are available for any project type and act as an extension to our Construction Management and Design-Build delivery methods. We hire and supervise all sub-contractors, as well as coordinate all job-site activities related to the construction of your project. We pride ourselves in exceeding all construction fundamentals: cost control, schedule control, quality control, sub-contractor management, communication and safety.</p>\n					</div>\n								</div>\n	</div>\n</div>\n\n	<div class=\"footer\">\n		<div class=\"footer-top\">\n			<div class=\"container\">\n				<div class=\"row\">\n					<div id=\"text-3\" class=\"widget widget_text col-md-4\"><h2 class=\"widget-title\"><span>GIZA E&#038;C., JSC</span></h2>			<div class=\"textwidget\"><p>Viglacera Building<br />\n671 Hoang Hoa Tham, Ba Dinh, Hanoi, Viet Nam</p>\n<p>Hotline: 1900 63 61 68<br />\nTel: (+84-24) 3247 4683<br />\nFax: (+84-24) 3247 4682<br />\nEmail: contact@giza.com.vn</p>\n<div id=\"fcb-call-button\">\n<p><a class=\"fcb-facebook\" href=\" https://www.facebook.com/gizacorporation/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><i class=\"fa fa-facebook\"></i> Facebook</a><a class=\"fcb-facebook\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCKkGPjjXx4fZ3FKbh1TqFHw\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><i class=\"fa fa-youtube\"></i> Youtube</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n		</div><div id=\"text-9\" class=\"widget widget_text col-md-4\"><h2 class=\"widget-title\"><span>The song of GIZA</span></h2>			<div class=\"textwidget\"><iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"203\" src=\"https://www